author: jparkerh
message:
Make the gpu_static_registration work properly

gpu_static_registration is intended to pull in all dependencies needed for the target - this ensures that this is the case.

PiperOrigin-RevId: 818820817

files.patch:
@@ -63,9 +63,11 @@ cc_library(
     name = "gpu_static_registration",
     srcs = ["gpu_static_registration.cc"],
     deps = [
+        ":xla_gpu_client_options",
         "//xla/pjrt/c:pjrt_c_api_gpu_internal",
         "//xla/pjrt/plugin:plugin_names",
         "//xla/pjrt/plugin:static_registration",
+        "//xla/service:gpu_plugin",
     ],
     alwayslink = True,
 )
